    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "okay fine, i'll check with a doctor eventually. but like, just for my own research, if someone were to follow a high-dose protocol like that, what would actually be the mechanism behind the \"loading dose\" idea people talk about? is there any scientific basis for using huge doses for a short period to raise levels quickly?",
